ear. Finally, as an application, we compute the\nPDFs of the two variables and compare with other forms in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jul 2014 03:47:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Nov 2014 06:17:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 30 Aug 2015 05:59:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2016 04:30:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-29"}
