ces could have for astrophysics, cosmology and\nfundamental physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jul 2014 13:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2014 10:01:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
